      },
      "date": "2019-11-01 05:53:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI've checked also OFD and MDT code and these flags are accessed always with checking o_valid first, I suppose we had some bad experience with that in past. I was thinking also about some wrapper with incorporated check for o_valid to get these flags, if you think it is reasonable it can be done.",
